nodes.text: A driver of a speeder was involved in a chase between Duchess Satine Kryze of the planet Mandalore and the Coruscant Security Force. Kryze was fleeing from CSF forces after being mistakenly identified as the murderer of Davu Golec of the Republic Ministry of Intelligence. Kryze ducked into an alley from which a driver in an airspeeder emerged a few seconds later. The driver was dressed with a hooded cloak similar to the Duchess. Believing the driver to be the Duchess, CSF pursued the driver, thus allowing Kryze to escape.
